    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with regular maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Come take a look and go for a spin; I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L V8 powerplant paired with a traditional 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically robust, exhibiting the characteristic high-revving induction note and a precise 8,400 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The Variable M Differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, while the Electronic Damping Control (EDC) system maintains chassis stability through high-frequency oscillations. The exterior displays minor aerodynamic stone chips and light wear commensurate with a spirited driver's car, but the structural integrity and powertrain remain uncompromised. An authentic, analog performance machine for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
