    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily practicality. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a deep gloss that catches the light, with only the slightest evidence of road use typical of a car that has been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free environment; the leather seating is supple with no rips or thinning, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have a complete folder of maintenance receipts to prove it. The engine pulls strongly without hesitation, and the transmission provides crisp, smooth shifts. We recently completed a full fluid flush and a professional detailing, so the car is truly turn-key and ready for its next owner. If you are looking for a reliable, high-quality ride that has been treated with respect, this is the one.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
